message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the sub-category for Sound and Music Computing, which is directly related to the topic of bird audio detection. Other likely sub-categories could include cs.CL (Computation and Language) for natural language processing, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) for image and video analysis, cs.LG (Machine Learning) for the use of neural networks, and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) for the overall topic of automated detection.
